00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:08.080
Exactamente.

00:24:08.680 --> 00:24:09.840
no quiero irme

00:24:11.560 --> 00:24:12.720
Me temo que Su Majestad

00:24:13.150 --> 00:24:14.960
