Una vez más.

00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:28.600
Tener confianza.

00:32:29.110 --> 00:32:30.040
Menear.

00:32:30.750 --> 00:32:31.800
De nuevo.

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:33.390
Menear.

